callee: SELECT oauth_applications.name, count(*) AS value FROM users LEFT JOIN oauth_applications ON oauth_applications.id = users.created_by_application_id WHERE users.created_at BETWEEN '2023-11-04 02:58:28.958826' AND '2023-11-06 02:58:28.959190' GROUP BY oauth_applications.name ORDER BY count(*) DESC LIMIT 10
